418
00:33:42,520 --> 00:33:46,081
When I'm sitting there at the drums,
I feel as though I'm in the right place.

419
00:33:46,257 --> 00:33:48,225
I feel as though I belong there.

420
00:33:50,728 --> 00:33:52,753
That's what I wanna do.

421
00:33:55,233 --> 00:33:58,760
