out of their lives that made them sad...

436
00:34:48,019 --> 00:34:49,418
...and lose them in music.

437
00:34:49,587 --> 00:34:52,181
And then they feel better afterwards.

438
00:34:55,393 --> 00:34:57,224
In a way, Mom...

439
00:34:57,862 --> 00:35:01,628
